- rule_name: SANCT_UNBOUNDED_STORAGE
  severity: Warning
  message: "SANCT_UNBOUNDED_STORAGE: `register` grows persistent collection `members` via `push_back` but never prunes entries or caps its length"
  location: "register:17"
  suggestion: "Cap `members.len()` before `push_back`, or remove/pop stale entries so the durable `members` entry cannot grow without bound"
- rule_name: SANCT_UNBOUNDED_STORAGE
  severity: Warning
  message: "SANCT_UNBOUNDED_STORAGE: `record_score` grows persistent collection `scores` via `set` but never prunes entries or caps its length"
  location: "record_score:29"
  suggestion: "Cap `scores.len()` before `set`, or remove/pop stale entries so the durable `scores` entry cannot grow without bound"
